---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Projects | Eliran Keren" description="Things I'm building — AI-native infrastructure for founders and operators.">
  <div class="projects-page">
    <h1>Projects</h1>
    <p class="intro">Things I'm building, experimenting with, and sharing publicly.</p>

    <section class="project" id="deeplica">
      <div class="project-header">
        <h2>🧠 Deeplica</h2>
        <div class="project-links">
          <a href="https://deeplica.ai" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Website</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p>
        A proactive second brain and coordination layer for knowledge workers. Deeplica doesn't just answer questions —
        it understands your priorities, closes open loops, and coordinates across your digital life.
        The goal: reduce cognitive overload and give people back time and mental clarity.
      </p>
      <div class="tech-stack">
        <span class="tech-tag">Agentic AI</span>
        <span class="tech-tag">Personal AI</span>
        <span class="tech-tag">Coordination Layer</span>
        <span class="tech-tag">Founder Tools</span>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="project" id="commander">
      <div class="project-header">
        <h2>⚡ Commander</h2>
        <div class="project-links">
          <a href="https://github.com/Elirank1" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p>
        An AI-powered founder OS built on Claude — a personal operating system that handles daily briefings,
        opportunity scouting, team task routing, and decision tracking. Commander runs as a scheduled
        autonomous agent: it reads signals, scores them, produces content when thresholds are met,
        and routes tasks to the right people — all without being asked.
      </p>
      <div class="tech-stack">
        <span class="tech-tag">Claude API</span>
        <span class="tech-tag">MCP</span>
        <span class="tech-tag">Agentic Workflows</span>
        <span class="tech-tag">Slack</span>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="project" id="ai-signals">
      <div class="project-header">
        <h2>📡 AI Signals</h2>
        <div class="project-links">
          <a href="https://elirank1.github.io/blog/blog" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Read</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p>
        A daily AI intelligence briefing — automatically researched, scored for relevance, written,
        and published every morning. Powered by Commander's Opportunity Scout: only signals that clear
        a narrative-fit and authority threshold make it to publication. Quality over volume.
      </p>
      <div class="tech-stack">
        <span class="tech-tag">Astro</span>
        <span class="tech-tag">MDX</span>
        <span class="tech-tag">GitHub Actions</span>
        <span class="tech-tag">Gemini</span>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="project" id="blog">
      <div class="project-header">
        <h2>✍️ This Blog</h2>
        <div class="project-links">
          <a href="https://github.com/Elirank1/blog" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p>
        A fast, minimal blog built with Astro and MDX. Dark mode, RSS feed, and a clean reading experience.
        The writing here is separate from the daily AI Signals — longer-form thinking on AI systems,
        founder workflows, and what happens when you stop maintaining the operating system of your own work.
      </p>
      <div class="tech-stack">
        <span class="tech-tag">Astro</span>
        <span class="tech-tag">TypeScript</span>
        <span class="tech-tag">MDX</span>
        <span class="tech-tag">GitHub Pages</span>
      </div>
    </section>

  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .projects-page { max-width: 800px; }
  .projects-page h1 { margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--color-heading); }
  .intro { font-size: 1.1rem; color: #6b7280; margin-bottom: 3rem; }

  .project {
    padding: 1.75rem;
    border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    border-radius: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    transition: border-color 0.2s ease;
  }
  .project:hover { border-color: #967FDB; }

  .project-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }
  .project-header h2 { margin: 0; font-size: 1.15rem; color: var(--color-heading); }

  .project-links { display: flex; gap: 1rem; }
  .project-links a {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #967FDB;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s ease;
  }
  .project-links a:hover { color: #7c5cbf; }

  .project p { color: #6b7280; font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.65; margin: 0 0 1rem; }

  .tech-stack { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.4rem; }
  .tech-tag {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
    border-radius: 9999px;
    background-color: #EDE9FE;
    color: #967FDB;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* Dark mode */
  [data-theme="dark"] .project { border-color: #1f1f2e; }
  [data-theme="dark"] .project:hover { border-color: #3d2e6e; }
  [data-theme="dark"] .project-header h2 { color: #e5e7eb; }
  [data-theme="dark"] .project p { color: #6b7280; }
  [data-theme="dark"] .tech-tag { background-color: #1E1538; color: #B8A4E8; }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .project { padding: 1.25rem; }
    .project-header { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
  }
</style>
